                    <locus target="#iir(ecto) #iiv(erso) #iiir(ecto) #iiiv(erso) #ivr(ecto) #ivv(erso)" facs="002 003 004 005">Fols. iir(ecto), iiv(erso), iiir(ecto), iiiv(erso), ivr(ecto), ivv(erso)</locus>
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                      Letter of Faith, Ṭomarä Haymanot, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጦማረ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</foreign>, a letter from Archbishop Marqos (VIII, 1797–1810), to the Church of Ethiopia, dealing with the Unctionist-Unionist debates. This work may have been copied by a different scribe (thus listed as a varia), and certainly with a different shade of red ink.
                      Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዛቲ፡ ጦማረ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘፈነዋ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘእስክንድርያ፡ ኀበ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ አብያተ፡ ክርስቲያናት፡ ዘኢትዮጵያ፡ በእዴሁ፡ ለጳጳስነ፡ መቃርዮስ፡ ሐዲስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስሌነ፡ አሜን። በስመ፡ አብ፡… ይቤ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ሳምናይ፡ እም፻ወ፯ ዘተሠዩ፡ እማርቆስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ እስከኒሁ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
